    "An internal error occurred, sorry! Visit https://actualbudget.org/contact/ for support. (ref: {{reason}})": "حدث خطأ داخلي، عذرًا! يرجى زيارة https://actualbudget.org/contact/ للحصول على الدعم (المرجع: {{reason}})",
